00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:14.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
back before it was uh still being considered as passable before it collapsed completely

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:17.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
