00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:51.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
which we think about that's patrolling the Mexican border, was actually formed to prevent Chinese

00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:58.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
from trying to sneak across from Mexico into the United States to avoid the 1882 laws.

00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:10.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
The 1882 law was passed to do two things: prevent Chinese from immigrating to the United States by their race, prevent them from becoming American citizens also by race.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:17.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
