00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:29.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
Expediant thing. And it was approved 10 years later in 1892.

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:34.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
