00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:22.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
you couldn't prevent Americans who people who were born in the United States bec- be American Citizens.

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:30.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
