00:32:28.000 --> 00:32:34.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Speaker 3</i>: My- in immigration records that I saw in San Bruno from my mother, big files like that,

00:32:34.000 --> 00:32:46.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
